													
													APPLY LEAVE SYSTEM
													------------------

ApplyLeaves is a UI based Front End Application. 
It uses LMSCore Application as a Rest call for all the database operations. 

Developed in = Spring MVC + MongoDB + Spring WebServices
Tools used 	 = Maven  +  Log4j2

Business Functionality : 
	1.	getLeaveBalance(Integer emp_id);
	2.	applyLeave();
	3.	cancelLeave();
	4.	updateLeave();	
	
	
Details about configuration: 
----------------------------
>>  All the jars dependency added through Maven. 
>>  Done all the Spring MVC configuration in /WEB-INF/spring-servlet.xml file.